<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Rotating Wheels</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Archivo:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&family=Baloo+Bhai+2:wght@400..800&family=Lobster&family=Montserrat:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&display=swap');

        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #000000, #03345a, #373434);
            color: white;
        }

        .video-background {
            position: relative;
            height: 100vh;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .video-background video {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100vh;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .video-content {
            position: absolute;
            z-index: 1;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            bottom: 0;
            right: 35%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
        }

        .video-content h1 {
            font-family: "Montserrat", sans-serif;
            font-size: 50px;
            color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        .video-content p {
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        .pause-btn {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 2%;
            right: 5%;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 20px;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 50%;
            z-index: 10;
        }

        .mute-btn {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 2%;
            right: 2%;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 20px;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 50%;
            z-index: 10;
        }


        .bioandprofile {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 70px;
            background-color: #ffff0059;
            padding: 100px 50px;
        }


        .profile-section {
            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
            position: relative;
        }

        .background-image {
            position: relative;
            height: 350px;
            width: 500px;
        }

        .slideshow img {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            height: 350px;
            width: 500px;
            object-fit: cover;
            object-position: center;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(26, 26, 25, 0.7);
            animation: fadeZoom 16s infinite;
            opacity: 0;
        }

        @keyframes fadeZoom {
            0% {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: scale(1);
            }

            5% {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: scale(1);
            }

            25% {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: scale(1);
            }

            30% {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: scale(1);
            }

            100% {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: scale(0.95);
            }
        }

        .slideshow img:nth-child(1) {
            animation-delay: 0s;
        }

        .slideshow img:nth-child(2) {
            animation-delay: 4s;
        }

        .slideshow img:nth-child(3) {
            animation-delay: 8s;
        }

        .slideshow img:nth-child(4) {
            animation-delay: 12s;
        }

        .profile-card {
            padding-bottom: 140px;
            border-radius: 80px 80px 20px 20px;
            margin-top: -85px;
            position: relative;
            background: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(26, 26, 25, 0.7);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .profile-card img {
            width: 140px;
            height: 140px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            object-fit: cover;
            border: 5px solid white;
            margin-top: -40px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(198, 61, 61, 0.5);

        }

        .name {
            font-size: 36px;
            margin: 30px 0 10px;
            color: #333;
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
        }

        .tagline {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #dc5c5c;
            font-weight: 500;
            overflow: hidden;
            white-space: nowrap;
            animation: typing 6s linear infinite;
            font-family: Verdana, Geneva, Tahoma, sans-serif;
        }

        @keyframes typing {
            0% {
                width: 0%;
            }

            25% {
                width: 50%;
            }

            50% {
                width: 100%;
            }

            75% {
                width: 50%
            }

            90% {
                width: 0%;
            }

            100% {
                width: 0%;
            }
        }

        .biography {
            margin: -10px;
        }

        .biography h1 {
            font-size: 50px;
            font-family: "Montserrat", sans-serif;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .biography div {
            margin-top: 10px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 15px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('navbar') %>

        <div class="video-background">
            <video src="/home/home1.mp4" autoplay muted loop id="bgVideo">Your browser does not support the video
                tag.</video>
            <div class="video-content">
                <h1>Rotating Wheels</h1>
                <p>Where the wheels turn stories begin</p>
            </div>
            <img src="/home/pause.svg" class="pause-btn" onclick="togglepause()">
            <img src="/home/mute.svg" class="mute-btn" onclick="toggleMute()">
        </div>

        <main>
            <div class="bioandprofile">
                <div class="profile-section">
                    <div class="background-image">
                        <div class="slideshow">
                            <img src="/images/culture-tradition-of-india.jpg">
                            <img src="/images/4714986_2491582.jpg">
                            <img src="/images/pexels-umkreisel-app-956999.jpg">
                            <img src="/images/default_profile.jpg">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="profile-card">
                        <img src="/images/4714986_2491582.jpg" alt="Profile Photo">
                        <h1 class="name">Mrinmoy</h1>
                        <p class="tagline">Explorer • Content Creator</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="biography" id="bio">
                    <h1>Biography</h1>
                    <hr>
                    <div>
                        <p>Ever since I first twisted the throttle of my Yamaha FZS V3, I knew the road would become my
                            second home. I’m Mrinmoy Das—a motovlogger, explorer, and storyteller who’s been riding
                            through
                            the heartbeats of India since 2021, capturing not just landscapes but memories etched in
                            motion
                            and emotion. What started as a casual ride turned into a lifelong passion, fueled by
                            curiosity
                            and a desire to see the country beyond the postcards. </p>

                        <p>My journey kicked off with humble beginnings, driven by a camera, a helmet, and an unshakable
                            spirit. Since then, I’ve roamed through the rolling hills of Meghalaya, the spiritual trails
                            of
                            Uttarakhand, the tropical serenity of the Andaman and Nicobar Islands, the cultural richness
                            of
                            Karnataka, and the lush green backwaters of Kerala. Each journey is not just about the
                            destination—it’s about the stories, the people, the roadside chai, and the occasional wrong
                            turn
                            that leads to the best adventures. </p>

                        <p>Traveling on two wheels is more than a lifestyle—it’s a commitment to simplicity, challenge,
                            and
                            raw experience. Riding through heavy rains in Cherrapunji, tracing winding hill roads in
                            Nainital, or breathing in the salty air of Havelock Island, every mile carries a new lesson.
                            And I’ve never been alone on this ride. My friends and even my parents have been a vital
                            part of
                            these journeys—making every trip a blend of adrenaline and warmth. </p>

                        <p>Since 2021, my blog and vlogs under the name “Rotating Wheels” have become more than
                            content—they’re a movement for those who want to explore but don’t know where to begin. I
                            document not just the beautiful destinations but also the real side of travel: the
                            breakdowns,
                            the strangers who become friends, the hidden food joints, and the soul-soothing silences on
                            deserted roads. </p>

                        <p>One of the most enriching aspects of my journey has been the interaction with local cultures.
                            I
                            believe in immersive travel—whether it’s tasting traditional cuisine. My goal is to showcase
                            the
                            diversity of India while inspiring people to respect and preserve it. </p>

                        <p>Whether you’re a biker, traveler, dreamer, or all of the above—welcome to my journey. This is
                            just the beginning. The wheels are still rotating, and the stories are still being written.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>
        <%- include('footer') %>
            <script>
                const togglepause = () => {
                    const video = document.getElementById('bgVideo');
                    const pauseBtn = document.querySelector('.pause-btn');

                    if (video.paused) {
                        video.play();
                        pauseBtn.src = '/home/pause.svg';
                    } else {
                        video.pause();
                        pauseBtn.src = '/home/play.svg';
                    }
                }
                const toggleMute = () => {
                    const video = document.getElementById('bgVideo');
                    video.muted = !video.muted;
                    document.querySelector('.mute-btn').src = video.muted ? `/home/mute.svg` : `/home/unmute.svg`;
                }
            </script>
</body>

</html>